### Why this order?

| Step | Tool              | Purpose                                      | Depe

# Tool Call Execution Plan

## Step 1 — Parallel Calls (no dependencies)

These two calls are independent and can be executed simultaneously:

```json
[
  {
    "tool": "get_weather",
    "params": {
      "city": "Tokyo"
    },
    "call_id": "call_1"
  },
  {
    "tool": "search_restaurants",
    "params": {
      "city": "Tokyo",
      "cuisine": "sushi"
    },
    "call_id": "call_2"
  }
]
```

## Step 2 — Sequential Call (depends on `call_2` results)

Once the restaurant search returns, use

